    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Failure Criteria"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Ratio of actual EGR flow rate to estimated normal EGR flow rate is less than 30% for more than 3.5 seconds."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Judgment is made by the ratio of the measured pressure fluctuation to the reference value of the intake manifold pressure fluctuation at the preset normal EGR flow rate."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "rows": [
